Tradingview regions traded securities

Source: R/trading_view.R
get_data_tradingview_regions_tickers.Rd

Acquires ticker symbols for specified regions

get_data_tradingview_regions_tickers(regions = c("america", "uk",
  "australia", "brazil", "canada", "euronext", "germany", "hongkong",
  "india", "japan", "mexico", "newzealand", "russia", "singapore", "spain",
  "switzerland", "taiwan", "turkey"), return_message = TRUE,
  nest_data = FALSE)

Arguments

regions

vector of regions

  • america

  • uk

  • australia

  • brazil

  • canada

  • euronext

  • germany

  • hongkong

  • india

  • japan

  • mexico

  • newzealand

  • russia

  • singapore

  • spain

  • switzerland

  • taiwan

  • turkey
return_message

if TRUE return message
